en_184938_0	The Sergeant Major who was arrested for carrying the hand grenade that exploded inside a bus in Kahagolla on 21st of February was remanded until 16th of March.
en_184938_1	He was arrested by Diyathalawa Police while he was receiving treatment at Diyathalawa Hospital and was produced before Bandarawela Magistrate.
en_184938_2	19 persons were injured in the explosion and 12 of them were security forces personnel.
